## List Views and Discovery

### Scan Your Community

The community list combines people, groups, and WhatsApp groups in one unified view, visually distinguished by color-coded rings. Infinite scroll loads twelve items at a time as you scroll, keeping the interface responsive even with thousands of records.

Sort by most recently updated to see who's been active. Filter by type to focus on just people, just groups, or just WhatsApp groups. Search to narrow down by name or identifier. The list updates in real-time as data changes—new signups appear without refreshing, status changes reflect immediately.

Each list item shows the avatar, name, status (for people), and how long ago the record was updated. Time formatting adapts to locale and recency: "2 hours ago," "yesterday," "3 weeks ago." These temporal cues help you identify stale records or recent activity at a glance.

